videos.headline: Vanderbilt gets the safety on muffed punt
videos.description: Richie James muffs punt return and recovers in endzone for a SAFETY

videos.headline: MTSU scores first touchdown of game
videos.description: Brent Stockstill pass complete to Richie James for 1 yd TD reception

videos.headline: Great run for Vanderbilt
videos.description: Ralph Webb hurdles the defender for a a 16 yard gain

videos.headline: Vanderbilt with the interception and long return
videos.description: Oren Burks intercepts the pass and returns it 59 yds to the MTnSt 7

videos.headline: Vandy adds to their lead
videos.description: Ralph Webb leaps over the pile for 1 yd TD run

videos.headline: MTSU with the blocked punt
videos.description: Sam Loy punt blocked by Azar Wilson and recovered by Canon Rooker

videos.headline: Blue Raiders cut into lead
videos.description: Ty Lee just gets his toes in for the 5 yd TD reception

videos.headline: Vanderbilt powers in for the score
videos.description: Ralph Webb breaks off to right for 3 yd TD run

videos.headline: Vandy scores again just before half
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur fires a pass to Kalija Lipscomb who takes a big hit and spins into endzone for the score

videos.headline: MTSU touchdown pass cuts lead to 33-24
videos.description: Brent Stockstill fires a perfect pass to Patrick Smith for 4 yd score

videos.headline: Vanderbilt looking to put game away after TD run
videos.description: Khari Blasingame bulls through for 1 yd TD
